OL,3,CFifty-eight officers injured in
OL,4,Cvehicle rammings in last year
OL,6,FAt least 58 police officers have been
OL,7,Finjured after their official vehicles
OL,8,Fwere deliberately rammed, the PSNI has
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,FThe officially recorded injuries were
OL,12,Fsustained in 40 rammings in the
OL,13,Fcalendar year to November 30.
OL,15,FHowever, the PSNI says the true total
OL,16,Fof officers hurt may be higher as
OL,17,Findividuals may have opted not to
OL,18,Freport their injuries and simply seek
OL,19,Ftreatment themselves.
