OL,4,Cvehicle rammings in last year
OL,6,FDeputy Chief Constable Bobby Singleton
OL,7,Fsaid: "In fact, many individuals who
OL,8,Fsustain injuries such as whiplash or
OL,9,Fsprains, often opt to remain on duty
OL,10,Fand to continue to serve their
OL,11,Fcommunities."
OL,13,FIncidents of police vehicles being
OL,14,Frammed occur more frequently in urban
OL,15,Fareas such as Belfast and Derry City,
OL,16,Fand also in border areas, as offenders
OL,17,Fattempt to flee from police.
