OL,6,FMr Singleton added: "Most vehicle
OL,7,Framming incidents occur as a result of
OL,8,Findividuals attempting to evade police
OL,9,For avoid arrest. This can be for a
OL,10,Frange of offences, from no insurance
OL,11,Fto more serious offending like robbery
OL,12,For assault.
OL,14,F"In these cases offenders are, in
OL,15,Fessence, using their vehicle as a
OL,16,Fweapon against us, and this is a scary
OL,17,Fand traumatising experience for any
OL,18,Fpolice officer to go through.
OL,26,@nD@UOUvD@AOU
