OL,6,F"It is a testament to the courage of
OL,7,Four people that they will put
OL,8,Fthemselves in situations where they
OL,9,Fare at risk, in order to protect
OL,10,Fcommunities from harm."
OL,12,FThe chairman of the Police Federation
OL,13,Ffor Northern Ireland, Liam Kelly, said
OL,14,Fthe figures were "shocking and
OL,15,Funacceptable" as members put their
OL,16,Flives at risk during their work.
