OL,3,CFifty-eight officers injured in
OL,4,Cvehicle rammings in last year
OL,6,FMr Kelly added: "Our men and women go
OL,7,Fout to do their best for this entire
OL,8,Fcommunity. For scores of them to be
OL,9,Fviciously targeted by those seeking to
OL,10,Fevade arrest or questioning is a
OL,11,Fworrying trend that must be stamped
OL,12,Fout.
OL,14,F"These reported figures are the tip of
OL,15,Fthe iceberg and I would encourage all
OL,16,Fofficers involved in such incidents,
OL,17,Fno matter the circumstances, to
OL,18,Fformally report what occurred so a
OL,19,Ftrue picture of the extent of this
OL,20,Fissue can be obtained."
