OL,6,FMore than #400,000 has been spent on
OL,7,Frepairing police vehicles damaged as a
OL,8,Fresult of being rammed in the past
OL,9,Ffive years, as the PSNI deals with
OL,10,Fongoing funding concerns.
OL,12,FMr Singleton said: "Finally, I need
OL,13,Fthose who would choose to deliberately
OL,14,Fram a police vehicle to understand the
OL,15,Fpotentially horrific consequences of
OL,16,Ftheir actions.
OL,18,F"The reality is that you could kill
OL,19,Fsomeone."
