OL,6,FHe added: "As police officers, we come
OL,7,Fto work knowing we could be faced with
OL,8,Fdifficult and dangerous situations,
OL,9,Fhowever, no one should ever have to
OL,10,Faccept a scenario in which their
OL,11,Fvehicle being rammed and them
OL,12,Fpotentially being injured or even
OL,13,Fkilled as a result is a reality of
OL,14,Ftheir work life. It simply wouldn't
OL,15,Fhappen in any other profession."
